<h2> Managing development of libraries</h2><h4><b>from:</b> <span class="ljuser with-alias-value ljuser-name_" lj:user="ext_333385" style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="http://www.livejournal.com/userinfo.bml?userid=32326384&amp;t=I"><img src="http://l-stat.livejournal.com/img/twitter-profile.gif?v=1" alt="[info]" width="16" height="16" style="vertical-align: bottom; border: 0; padding-right: 1px;" /></a><a href="http://twitter.com/jorgetavares"><b>jorgetavares</b></a></span><br />
